  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The pragmatic issue at hand how to get physicians and nurses to use best practicesâ€¦ and how
      to measure consequences of their implementation. This is the science of &quot;knowledge
      translation&quot;, which we are realizing is an &quot;organic&quot; entity. As part of our Critical Care
      Strategy our goal is to improve the quality and continuity of critical care within our health
      care system. Toward this goal we are implementing a program which links 16 Ontario hospitals
      through their critical care units in a Provincial Network.
    </textblock>
